{"h52cc8012gf11ag4a4cg9f00gb575de681dfc": ["Please, just leave me in peace.", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "895169ba-3d0b-c720-9379-cf60bc8ca1bd"], "hf1d58ecfgc384g4547g8e37gef988ce1d582": ["Or what? You'll kill me? Tell your snakes to rip out my throat? ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "5497c490-4791-e3bd-73d3-ce1e92e707b0"], "h6eed6a2bg78c3g472eg8058gaa6968e1ae28": ["She was just a <i>child.</i>", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "2c189cd2-8c0c-f56b-e907-15716ef53ad1"], "he550d5a2g24eeg46b1gb52cg6f682219633e": ["A terrible tragedy. I am so very sorry.", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "3be738ac-c136-4da5-95d1-a8eed258acb8"], "he28798b6ga86eg4eb5gaef9g85d67fc36041": ["You will be once I'm done with you. ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "119d0be5-8268-2f85-e95f-60a47f785ea0"], "hb762879cg36d7g472ag95f2gf4d248e0eee6": ["I swear to you, I gave Teela no order to strike.", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "6ee9731a-6d3d-fb78-e60e-0ca161d16d4e"], "h7c3283degdd08g4c0ega789ga266dc160343": ["You're a liar.", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "be535f1f-c330-e676-6f32-7ee0d7489a40"], "h295fd95eg4c49g48afg99beg664ab166569d": ["Our daughter is dead because of you! ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "df53bbe6-1181-513c-2b5b-6736e9a2cb19"], "h10f6c07eg198cg4d19g8319gef64d0e02868": ["You're trying my patience. Get out of my sight.", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "f92fbd8a-16e3-e7d4-5a16-984b6021a9f0"], "h2f5b813cgd3c4g4340gb0a3gd3c934afaf79": ["Then you should have kept her in line. You've only yourselves to blame.", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "1f28bb48-57c8-32af-cc2d-9ade957e6914"], "hb0ed33aag32acg48c9g8a0cg4990b86afcef": ["Hah. You have no idea what's about to happen - do you? ", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "e10b27e6-ca1d-f9b5-605a-f164966f3461"], "h31f20921g6a65g4fe1gb567gcb8ca0bf0adb": ["You loosed a thug in my grove. What did you expect to happen?", "95eb2b0b-a522-4ea5-8167-c5f4d1418156", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "b3fb880d-9d0a-9055-fe6b-42e3901ff2aa"], "hf27537cfg1f9cg45d2g90a2g898bdfeb94ce": ["You <i>murdered</i> our daughter. ", "d6d88c8b-6ba7-4350-b3b3-d60565a44e90", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "2b0b5469-c06d-20c1-3868-8565f7f74c66"], "he5f15b0agd229g43f3g8957g87bdb558633c": ["Did you think we'd let you go? Let you walk away?", "397467d4-1631-447b-a505-d44275dca78e", ".\\voicebarks\\Camp\\NPCs\\ADs\\CAMP_GoblinHuntCelebration_AD_ParentsAndDruidLeader.html", "e70166d1-3e02-1f31-2029-f211f47f6af2"]}